# COMMERCEBOARD
 
POST AN AD, RESPOND TO AN AD!  OPERATORS ASK PEOPLE TO POST ADS!

OPERATORS CAN FACILITATE INTERACTION BETWEEN PEOPLE USING TRASH MAGIC HYPERSIGNS FOR ADS AS WELL!

PEOPLE CAN POST A HYPERSIGN AND ALSO MAKE A PHYSICAL ONE AND OPERATORS CAN EXCHANGE THEM, PICKING THEM UP AND DROPPING THEM OFF.  THEY ALL ALSO HAVE A VIRTUAL IMAGE, WHICH CAN BE USED TO REPLICATE THE PHYSICAL ONE AND VICE VERSA!

THE BOARDS ARE THE COLLECTION OF HYPERSIGNS!
